      • getState

        public String getState()
        Get product purchasing state.
        Returns:
        product purchasing state (not the same thing as order state)
        • "ordering" - creating order
        • "ordered" - order created
        • "paying" - payment UI operation ongoing
        • "cancelled" - cancelled by user
        • "accepted" - payment accepted by channel server
        • "confirming" - confirming order state
        • "succeeded" - payment succeeded
        • "cheated" - money received less than order price
        • "failed" - payment failed
        • "delivering" - delivering
        • "delivered" - delivered
